import pandas as pd
import seaborn as sns
url = "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/pic16b-ucla/24W/main/datasets/palmer_penguins.csv"
penguins = pd.read_csv(url)


penguins = penguins.set_index(['Sample Number'])
penguins = penguins[['Body Mass (g)', 'Flipper Length (mm)', 'Species']]


sns.scatterplot(penguins, x = 'Body Mass (g)', y = 'Flipper Length (mm)', hue = 'Species').set(title='Flipper Length and Body Mass relationships in three species of penguins')
plt.legend(bbox_to_anchor=(1, 1),loc=2)

from matplotlib import pyplot as plt
url = "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/pic16b-ucla/24W/main/datasets/palmer_penguins.csv"
